      {
        "text": "Ivanti Connect Secure and Ivanti Policy Secure contain a vulnerability that allows a remote, authenticated attacker to write arbitrary files. These vulnerabilities are addressed in Ivanti Connect Secure version 22.7R2.6 and Ivanti Policy Secure version 22.7R1.3.",
        "title": "Risk Evaluation",
        "category": "summary"
      },
      {
        "text": "These vulnerabilities are addressed by Ivanti Connect Secure version 22.7R2.6 and Ivanti Policy Secure version 22.7R1.3. The latest version of these products can be downloaded from the [Ivanti Licensing Portal](https://portal.ivanti.com/).",
        "title": "Recommended Practices",
        "category": "general"
      },
